---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy | Solvanta Pay"
  description="Privacy policy placeholder for Solvanta Pay. Have counsel review before collecting production data."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="muted"><strong>Draft placeholder — not legal advice.</strong> Review with qualified counsel before launch.</p>
      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Outline the categories of personal data collected through the website and application forms (e.g., contact details,
        business information).
      </p>
      <h2>How we use data</h2>
      <p>Describe operational uses such as underwriting review, communication, and regulatory obligations.</p>
      <h2>Retention</h2>
      <p>Describe retention periods and deletion practices.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Add a privacy contact channel.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
